<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277698>
    bibo:endPage "64" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "53" ;
    bibo:volume "2896" ;
    dc:creator "Callaghan, Curtis John; Llorente-Bousquets, Jorge" ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "A new Mexican Mesene (Lepidoptera, Riodinidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277699>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277700>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277701>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277702> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277699>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 15. 1, 2 Mesene jimena sp. nov. Holotype male, dorsal, ventral; 3,4 Mesene jimena sp. nov., female, dorsal, ventral; 5 – 14 Mesene margaretta variation. 5. male Chiapas, Mexico, dorsal, 6. ventral; 7. female Chiapas, dorsal, 8. ventral; 9. male, Palmichal, Caribobo, Venezuela, dorsal, 10. ventral; 11. Río Cangua, Barinas, Venezuela, male dorsal, 12. ventral; 13. female Cuyagua, Aragua, Venezuela, 14. ventral. Fig. 15 Mesene margaretta, male resting beneath leaf, Mexico." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277699/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277700>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 21. Male genitalia: 16 Mesene jimena sp. nov., lateral view, aedeagus removed; 17 Mesene jimena sp. nov., aedeagus showing position of retracted vesica; 18. Mesene jimena sp. nov. ventral view, aedeagus removed; 19. Mesene margaretta lateral view, aedeagus removed; 20. Mesene margaretta, lateral view with vesica extended; 21. Mesene margaretta male, ventral view, aedeagus removed. Bar is 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277701>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 26. Female genitalia: 22. Mesene jimena sp. nov. ventral view; 23. Mesene jimena sp. nov. lateral view; 24. Mesene margaretta ventral view; 25. Detail of ostium bursae; 26. Mesene margaretta, lateral view. Bar is 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277701/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277702>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Distribution map of Mesene jimena sp. nov. () and Mesene margaretta () in México. X dry barriers." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277702/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

